{
  "stem": "26699.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He tried three times to settle in Israel-- actually which was Palestine in those times-- and harder he tried, he never managed to establish himself, and came back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the last time when he came back, he actually came during the First World War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was taken to the army, he fought against the Germans in the First World War, got sick of typhus, and came at home very sick, almost dying.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when he saw that he would be a burden for his family, he took his life by shooting himself with the same weapon that was given to him for the front line.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My grandmother then had to sustain the whole family of six children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my schooling started during the war, so there were a lot of events which happened in this period of time in Romania, and actually in the whole Europe, in those times.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My schooling time started in 1941, when I was six years and three months old, four months old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those times, the Jews of course went through a very traumatic time a year before, and their lives were in great danger.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All kind of laws and regulations were issued, and the Jewish children were not allowed, in the whole country of Romania, to attend public schools.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were banned from the public schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I do remember, while passing with my mother in front of a public school, and ask her when I'm going to attend the school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, unfortunately, you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're not allowed to attend this school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the Jewish community in Iasi-- I have to say that it was almost 50% of the whole population of this town was Jewish, like many other towns in Moldavia.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
